WEBVTT

00:00.001 --> 00:01.674
<i>Previously on "Faking It"...</i>

00:01.709 --> 00:05.794
You did the one thing
you knew I could never forgive.

00:05.796 --> 00:07.579
This is where you decide
whether or not

00:07.580 --> 00:08.797
- I'll be in your life anymore.
- Wait.

00:08.799 --> 00:10.499
- Was any of it real?
- No.

00:10.501 --> 00:11.883
You're done
with the art nonsense.

00:11.885 --> 00:14.720
You'll start an internship
at Skwerkel instead.

00:14.722 --> 00:16.838
You know Liam
did this, right?

00:16.840 --> 00:19.558
Apparently someone sent a link
of Duke's double account to TMZ.

00:19.560 --> 00:21.476
I am in love
with Shane Harvey.

00:21.478 --> 00:22.761
Thank you all for your support.

00:22.763 --> 00:25.058
I can't wait
to be your president.

00:25.766 --> 00:27.981
- Does this mean you forgive me?
- No.

00:34.942 --> 00:37.159
I love you.

00:38.829 --> 00:40.028
What are you doing?

00:40.030 --> 00:42.164
I'm sorry.
It just slipped out.

00:42.166 --> 00:43.615
How many times
do I have to tell you,

00:43.617 --> 00:45.834
we're just good buddies
who occasionally have sex.

00:45.836 --> 00:49.621
And if that's too confusing for
you, then maybe we should stop.

00:49.623 --> 00:50.922
Yeah. Yeah, I get it.

00:50.924 --> 00:53.091
My mouth just forgot.

00:55.796 --> 00:57.012
[bleep].

00:57.014 --> 00:59.047
We're going to be late.

00:59.049 --> 01:01.266
To be continued.

01:03.354 --> 01:06.138
Just give me a sec.

01:08.942 --> 01:11.893
Lauren?
Are you okay?

01:11.895 --> 01:14.646
It's been two weeks since
you broke up with that boy.

01:14.648 --> 01:15.697
Who? What boy?

01:15.699 --> 01:18.200
Oh, that Theo guy?
I barely knew him.

01:18.202 --> 01:21.319
If that's true,
then why are you so angry?

01:21.321 --> 01:23.288
I'm not angry.
I'm stressed.

01:23.290 --> 01:25.240
As class president,
I'm now a role model,

01:25.242 --> 01:27.042
which means I can't be late.

01:27.044 --> 01:29.995
So tell Amy
she can take the bus.

01:29.997 --> 01:31.830
Amy!
You've got five seconds

01:31.832 --> 01:34.633
till I come up there
and drag you out of bed!

01:34.635 --> 01:36.385
I'm here. Jeez.

01:36.387 --> 01:38.336
If you want to ride with Lauren,
she just left.

01:38.338 --> 01:41.590
Oh, it's okay. Karma and Liam
are picking me up.

01:41.592 --> 01:45.010
Darling, I know I haven't
been the best model

01:45.012 --> 01:46.845
for healthy relationships,

01:46.847 --> 01:49.147
but even I can tell
that's a terrible idea.

01:49.149 --> 01:51.183
Karma and I spent the past two
weeks talking everything out,

01:51.185 --> 01:53.852
and she's totally forgiven me
for sleeping with Liam.

01:53.854 --> 01:55.320
I hope you're right.

01:55.322 --> 01:58.576
But if she comes at you
with a sharp object, run.

02:02.112 --> 02:05.247
♪ Walking down the sidewalk ♪

02:05.249 --> 02:09.451
♪ Is that the way
that you want to be seen? ♪

02:13.090 --> 02:14.956
Oh, is that Reagan?

02:14.958 --> 02:16.875
Let me guess.
Did she propose?

02:16.877 --> 02:18.343
Very funny.

02:18.345 --> 02:21.346
No, she texted a pic
from our camping trip.

02:21.348 --> 02:23.348
That's not at all
how I pictured it.

02:23.350 --> 02:25.684
Not that I pictured
anything.

02:28.388 --> 02:30.222
It was really nice of you
to drive us to school today.

02:30.224 --> 02:31.890
What can I say?

02:31.892 --> 02:33.525
I'm a good buddy.

02:33.527 --> 02:37.562
And plus, this way I can keep
an eye on you two.

02:39.399 --> 02:41.900
I am kidding, guys.
Jeez.

02:41.902 --> 02:43.618
I told you, I'm over it.

02:43.620 --> 02:46.071
Let it go.

02:46.073 --> 02:49.241
Karma, are you sure
you're over it?

02:49.243 --> 02:50.709
What?
Why do you ask?

02:50.711 --> 02:53.628
I just sense this edge
in your voice,

02:53.630 --> 02:55.547
and you're still not wearing
your friendship necklace.

02:55.549 --> 02:57.382
Oh, are we still
doing that?

02:57.384 --> 03:01.920
I mean, don't you think
they're a little childish?

03:01.922 --> 03:05.090
We are 16.
We've already been arrested.

03:05.092 --> 03:07.926
And we're not virgins anymore,
thanks to this guy.

03:07.928 --> 03:10.896
Trust me.
So over it.

03:12.816 --> 03:15.433
Look at me,
a professional MMA fighter

03:15.435 --> 03:18.436
holding hands in public
with a super-hot boyfriend.

03:18.438 --> 03:20.739
See? Stars...
they're just like us.

03:20.741 --> 03:24.109
It's almost like whoever
outed you did you a favor.

03:24.111 --> 03:27.662
Almost, except that bitter,
little dickwad didn't realize

03:27.664 --> 03:30.081
that when Cluck-N-Go dropped me,
Swiftly would come to my rescue.

03:30.083 --> 03:31.700
If I ever find out
who he is...

03:31.702 --> 03:34.369
Okay, Dukey,
save it for the ring.

03:34.371 --> 03:36.371
I'm sorry. You're right.

03:36.373 --> 03:38.623
You always know
how to talk me down.

03:44.882 --> 03:48.850
You okay? I'm being all shrimpy,
and you seem distracted.

03:48.852 --> 03:52.637
You're hiding something.
I think I know what it is.

03:52.639 --> 03:54.472
You do?

03:54.474 --> 03:55.807
Yeah. Lauren got elected
class president over you.

03:55.809 --> 03:59.444
She's played
the inter-sex card, okay?

03:59.446 --> 04:01.813
The school will turn on her
when they see her radical...

04:01.815 --> 04:03.031
agenda.

04:03.033 --> 04:05.367
All right, you're next.
Step forward, please.

04:06.787 --> 04:09.287
Student IDs, please.

04:09.289 --> 04:10.822
Uh, I threw mine away
last year.

04:10.824 --> 04:12.874
Horrible pic. I tried this new
eyebrow-raise thing,

04:12.876 --> 04:14.075
and it did not work.

04:14.077 --> 04:16.327
Penny, we got another one.

04:16.329 --> 04:18.413
It's okay.
This young man is a student.

04:18.415 --> 04:20.165
What about this yahoo?

04:20.166 --> 04:21.666
Uh, he's not a student.

04:21.668 --> 04:25.220
This is my professional
MMA fighter boyfriend.

04:25.222 --> 04:26.638
Now I've seen everything.

04:26.640 --> 04:29.307
Penelope,
what the [bleep] was that?

04:29.309 --> 04:31.059
I know. I'm sorry.

04:31.061 --> 04:32.677
Trust me,
I didn't hire him.

04:32.679 --> 04:33.979
Then who did?

04:33.981 --> 04:36.731
The new principal.

04:36.766 --> 04:41.186
Sync and corrections by explosiveskull
www.addic7ed.com

04:41.221 --> 04:42.687
This is
a perfect opportunity

04:42.689 --> 04:44.656
to prop up your softening
poll numbers.

04:44.658 --> 04:47.692
What are you talking about?
People love me.

04:47.694 --> 04:50.412
People love the idea of you.
The reality? Not so much.

04:50.414 --> 04:51.780
Everyone had hopes

04:51.782 --> 04:54.366
that you would be a more
inspirational leader.

04:54.368 --> 04:56.751
Perhaps if you talked more
about being inter-sex.

04:56.753 --> 04:57.869
Zip.

04:57.871 --> 05:00.956
Okay, then talk
about how Theo betr...

05:00.958 --> 05:03.041
Zip.
We discussed this.

05:03.043 --> 05:05.093
Public figure,
private person.

05:05.095 --> 05:06.294
Okay.

05:06.296 --> 05:08.213
Then your only other option

05:08.215 --> 05:10.215
is to stand up
to this new principal.

05:10.217 --> 05:12.183
Rally the school
behind you.

05:12.185 --> 05:13.551
I'm sorry, Wendy.

05:13.553 --> 05:15.637
We'll have to pause
this conversation.

05:15.639 --> 05:18.390
Someone is sitting
at our table.

05:18.392 --> 05:19.724
Pipe down, Evita.

05:19.726 --> 05:22.444
There are no reserved tables
in the cafeteria.

05:22.446 --> 05:25.030
There are now.
I enacted the measure last week.

05:25.032 --> 05:27.565
So, if you don't mind...

05:28.631 --> 05:30.402
You know what, Lauren?
I'm so glad

05:30.404 --> 05:31.870
you have something
to cling to

05:31.872 --> 05:34.623
since Theo's tragic betrayal.

05:34.625 --> 05:37.492
But don't forget who really
calls the shots around here... me.

05:38.912 --> 05:40.629
Oh, Shane.

05:40.631 --> 05:43.048
Bitter really suits you.

05:45.836 --> 05:47.168
Hey.

05:47.170 --> 05:48.720
- Can we talk about Karma?
- Can we talk about Karma?

05:48.722 --> 05:50.388
- You go.
- You go. Ladies first.

05:50.390 --> 05:52.424
- I will cut you.
- Then I'll go first.

05:52.426 --> 05:54.976
Karma says that she's forgiven
us, but I don't think she has.

05:54.978 --> 05:57.929
I know. She called
these necklaces childish.

05:57.931 --> 05:59.898
Well, she has a point.

05:59.900 --> 06:01.266
Didn't you win them
playing Skee-Ball?

06:01.268 --> 06:03.268
No. It was the claw machine.

06:03.270 --> 06:05.070
Attention, all students,

06:05.072 --> 06:07.322
please make your way to the quad
for a mandatory assembly.

06:07.324 --> 06:08.823
- Ladies first.
- Ugh!

06:10.527 --> 06:13.828
Gandhi once said
the best way to find yourself

06:13.830 --> 06:15.447
is to lose yourself
in service.

06:15.449 --> 06:18.616
And I look forward to serving
you as Hester's new...

06:18.618 --> 06:21.536
Vice principal.

06:21.538 --> 06:23.672
As of today,
we have a new leader...

06:23.674 --> 06:25.290
Principal Turner.

06:25.292 --> 06:26.758
What's the deal?

06:26.760 --> 06:28.960
Thank you,
Vice Principal Beaver.

06:28.962 --> 06:30.462
It's Bevier.

06:30.464 --> 06:31.796
Kids, I'll be honest
with you.

06:31.798 --> 06:34.015
I am not
an inspirational leader.

06:34.017 --> 06:36.051
I'm not here to tell you
to dream big

06:36.053 --> 06:39.604
or reach for the stars
or any of that bullcrap.

06:39.606 --> 06:43.108
The recent drug bust
exposed a school

06:43.110 --> 06:45.110
with dangerously loose
academic standards

06:45.112 --> 06:47.028
and a complete disregard

06:47.030 --> 06:48.980
for how things are done
in the real world.

06:48.982 --> 06:50.398
I am here to fix that.

06:50.400 --> 06:52.617
Trust that it's for
your own good.

06:56.123 --> 06:58.406
Lauren Cooper,
sophomore class president.

06:58.408 --> 06:59.791
You must let me
give you a tour.

06:59.793 --> 07:01.626
And, no, I won't take no
for an answer.

07:01.628 --> 07:03.078
We got to stop this guy.

07:03.080 --> 07:05.163
Let's meet after school
and come up with a plan.

07:05.165 --> 07:07.499
Uh, I can't today.
I've got to go to the dentist.

07:07.501 --> 07:09.000
This is important.

07:09.002 --> 07:10.668
I heard he turned the art studio
into a storage room.

07:10.670 --> 07:11.920
And I'm really
upset about it.

07:11.922 --> 07:13.671
But he books up
weeks in advance.

07:13.673 --> 07:15.890
Penelope.

07:15.892 --> 07:17.475
That guy's going
to destroy everything

07:17.477 --> 07:18.843
this school stands for.

07:18.845 --> 07:20.395
You don't think
that I know that?

07:20.397 --> 07:22.680
But I barely kept my job,
and I have three cats to feed.

07:22.682 --> 07:24.482
I'm sorry.
There's nothing I can do.

07:24.484 --> 07:26.985
But if a certain
student leader

07:26.987 --> 07:29.354
were to rally the school
in protest.

07:29.356 --> 07:31.156
Okay, I'm blushing.
Stop.

07:31.158 --> 07:33.024
- I'll do it.
- You're gonna talk to Lauren.

07:33.026 --> 07:36.327
Thank you. I got to keep
my hands clean.

07:36.329 --> 07:37.779
You want to talk
about what's wrong?

07:37.781 --> 07:39.497
Well, let's see.

07:39.499 --> 07:42.367
Now I'm not just the girl
who lied about being a lesbian,

07:42.369 --> 07:44.536
I'm also the daughter
of the drug dealers

07:44.538 --> 07:45.837
who destroyed the school.

07:45.839 --> 07:48.506
- So fun.
- You're having feelings.

07:48.508 --> 07:49.924
How about I'll come over
after school

07:49.926 --> 07:51.626
and we'll eat them
together?

07:51.628 --> 07:53.711
Isn't today your mom's
meatless meat loaf Monday?

07:53.713 --> 07:56.598
Oh, uh, that got canceled.

07:56.600 --> 07:58.466
Mom's got
a really bad hangnail.

07:58.468 --> 07:59.934
It's infected.

07:59.936 --> 08:01.970
Trust me, you don't want
her hands in your food.

08:01.972 --> 08:03.221
Bye.

08:03.223 --> 08:04.939
Skwerkel Headquarters.
Please hold.

08:04.941 --> 08:07.392
- Hey, Liam!
- Hey, Janet.

08:07.394 --> 08:10.111
- How's your husband's bunion?
- Doctor says it isn't infected.

08:10.113 --> 08:12.897
Oh, good.
I was worried.

08:12.899 --> 08:15.116
We meet again,
young Jedi.

08:16.820 --> 08:19.070
I'll never join you
on the Dark Side.

08:19.072 --> 08:20.238
We'll see.

